kgmoji\" />唔係以為（自稱）黃色就咩都做得呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyZTT5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyZTT5h.jpg&h=d6c394ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcLcqbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcLcqbY.jpg&h=50e3c1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1UAnYE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1UAnYE.png&h=15043109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsteve寫話捐錢都好信，到時佢唔捐又好似果80萬咁落咗格，好似佢啲卡game咁成年幾都唔發貨，你係味想咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且佢都係寫捐612呢d大路，我不如自己捐咗佢算<br />\n味見過邊間黃店咁大口氣用手足價三個字，龍門渣哥做咁多野都唔叫自己良店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要同出邊個價冇分別咁咪即係普通做生意，用咩鬼手足價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">水貨化妝品都當黃店咁金鋪都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊度黃啊企開啲啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"100a52071b02635cfffb471bbf5e3e9fb7587dfd","tid":1828463,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T00:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b16c562dd448f168a9df5e091e2d1eec7d4a3a","tid":1828463,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:00:54.000Z","msg":"香港要你"},{"pid":"afdfdba251ee675e502fe4a903847746cfcbd9e1","tid":1828463,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f56b7b5f62a9816478c6fd8e3031346e4a22f55","tid":1828463,"uid":265839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"咁耐先新增4宗&hellip;真唔真呀<br />\n定係已經大爆發咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"中國：全部人都有事 姐係無事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /